sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OnlineSvc as Online Feature Server<br/>6566/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant RegistrySvc as Registry Server<br/>6570/TCP gRPC<br/>6572/TCP REST
    participant OfflineSvc as Offline Store Server<br/>8815/TCP
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Operator as Feast Operator<br/>8081/TCP health
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob
    participant Notebook as Kubeflow Notebook

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval
    Client->>Route: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Route->>OnlineSvc: Forward request<br/>HTTP(S)/6566, Bearer JWT (optional)
    OnlineSvc->>Redis: Fetch features<br/>TCP/6379, Password auth
    Redis-->>OnlineSvc: Feature values
    OnlineSvc-->>Route: JSON response
    Route-->>Client: Feature response

    Note over CronJob,PG: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)
    CronJob->>OfflineSvc: feast materialize-incremental<br/>In-process
    OfflineSvc->>PG: Read from offline store<br/>TCP/5432, Password auth
    PG-->>OfflineSvc: Historical feature data
    OfflineSvc->>Redis: Write to online store<br/>TCP/6379, Password auth
    Redis-->>OfflineSvc: ACK

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>Operator: FeatureStore CR event<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployments,<br/>Services, ConfigMaps<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Operator->>RegistrySvc: GET /api/v1/permissions<br/>HTTP(S), Bearer JWT (intra-comm HMAC-SHA256)
    RegistrySvc-->>Operator: Permissions list
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create dynamic RBAC<br/>ClusterRoles, RoleBindings

    Note over Notebook,OnlineSvc: Flow 4: Notebook Integration
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Notebook CR event<br/>(kubeflow.org/v1)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>with Feast client config
    Notebook->>OnlineSvc: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTP(S)/6566, Bearer JWT (optional)
    OnlineSvc-->>Notebook: Feature response
